name: Yule Ooze
oracle_text:
At the beginning of your upkeep, destroy another nonland permanent chosen at random, then put a number of +1/+1 counters on Yule Ooze equal to that permanent's converted mana cost.
{R}{G}, Eat some food: Regenerate Yule Ooze.
flavor_text: It loves having family for dinner.

name: Stocking Tiger
oracle_text:
Stocking Tiger enters with a sealed Magic booster pack under it.
When Stocking Tiger deals combat damage to a player, unwrap the booster pack and put it into your hand.
flavor_text: Just hope yours isn't full of coal golems.

name: Topdeck the Halls
oracle_text:
Decorated cards in your hand have miracle {S}. (Decorated cards include premiums, promos, and cards with alternate frames or art.)
At the beginning of your upkeep, if you control twelve or more decorated permanents, you win the game.

name: Goblin Sleigh Ride
oracle_text: Target creature you control climbs into Goblin Sleigh Ride. You slide them on their merry way. If the creature stayed on, it deals damage equal to its toughness to each other creature touched during the slide.
flavor_text: "What fun it is to ride and sing a slaying song tonight!"

name: Some Disassembly Required
oracle_text: {B}, Sacrifice a creature: Distribute the sacrificed creature's keyword abilities among any number of other target creatures until end of turn. If it's December, you gain 1 life for each of those keywords.
flavor_text: Now all they needed was a jolly, happy soul.

name: Seasonal Sequels

flavor_text: NOW SHOWING: *Sword of Hearth and Home Alone*, *Eight Crazy Knights' Charge*, *Holiday Incinerate*, and *Phyrexian Gremlins*.

name: Last-Minute Chopping
oracle_text: Ask target opponent if they remembered to get you a present. If they say yes, they put a card they own from outside the game into your hand. Otherwise, you gain control of target permanent they control.
flavor_text: "Dear brother, I couldn't forget you if I tried, and I *have* tried."

name: Eggnogger's 'Stache
oracle_text:
Lands you control have "{T}: Refill your mug with a festive drink." (If you don't have a mug, go grab a mug! It's the holidays!)
At the beginning of combat on your turn, if you have a drink 'stache, put two +1/+1 counters on each creature you control.
flavor_text: Blend dingus egg yolks, milk, Eldraine spice blend, Muragandan vanilla, and absolutely nothing else.

card_faces.name: Decorated Knight
card_faces.oracle_text: Whenever Decorated Knight attacks, draw a card from your original deck if it's outside the game.

card_faces.name: Present Arms
card_faces.oracle_text: Exchange your library with another deck you own from outside the game. Shuffle your library.

card_faces.name: Naughty
card_faces.oracle_text: Search another target player's library for a card and put that card into your hand. Then shuffle that player's library.

card_faces.name: Nice
card_faces.oracle_text: Search your library for a card and put it into another target player's hand. Then shuffle your library.

name: Thopter Pie Network
oracle_text:
At the beginning of your upkeep, if you're eating, create a 1/1 colorless Thopter artifact creature token with flying. Use food to represent the token.
Whenever a creature token you control dies, if it's represented by food, eat it.
flavor_text: They all thought her dream was just pie in the sky.

oracle_text:
Flying

name: Evil Presents
oracle_text: Put a creature card from your hand into play under target opponent's control. That creature attacks each turn if able . . . and always attacks its controller.
flavor_text: 'Tis better to give than to receive.

oracle_text:
Whenever a creature deals damage to you, put a globe counter on it.
{T}, {Q}, {T}, {Q}, {T}: Tap all creatures with globe counters on them.
flavor_text: WARNING: Shake gently. Contents may cause choking, hypothermia, and/or planar invasion.

name: Fruitcake Elemental
oracle_text:
Fruitcake Elemental is indestructible.
At the end of your turn, Fruitcake Elemental deals 7 damage to you.
{3}: Target player gains control of Fruitcake Elemental.
flavor_text: Experiments intended to create the perfect holiday emissary resulted in a substance harder than darksteel and a fraction as merry.

name: Mishra's Toy Workshop
oracle_text: {T}: Add {C}{C}{C}. Spend this mana only on spells and abilities that put tokens onto the battlefield. Use toys to represent the tokens.
flavor_text: Even though Urza tried to apologize, Mishra continued to bear a grudge.

name: Season's Beatings
oracle_text: Family gathering — Each creature target player controls deals damage equal to its power to another random creature that player controls.
flavor_text: Arriving home, he suddenly longed for the bloodsoaked battlefields behind him.

name: Chaos Wrap
oracle_text: The owner of target permanent shuffles it into their library. Then they may look at the top card of their library and may wrap it. If it's a permanent card, they may put it onto the battlefield. Otherwise, they may put it onto the battlefield face down as a 4/4 red Present creature. (To wrap a card, put it inside lots of sleeves. If it would be dealt damage or destroyed, remove a sleeve from it instead.)
